Summary: The object blacked out the whole sky while it passed over, completely silent. The rear had lights whereas you could see people walking inside craft multi floors.
trends: There have been 116 other sightings in Dallas
There were no other sightings in Dallas on or around May 26th 1995
divs: Sighting DetailsI was outside after a storm, I had looked up and noticed how clear it was. Then it became abnormally quiet, I looked up and now the sky was black, I continued looking up and while black it had motion the object was gigantic I could not determine width nor length but when the craft passed There were "people" moving around that were visible on multi levels The back of craft had windows, opaque in nature but still shapes were visible . the craft was at least 60' in depth I couldn't see the front or sides it took minutes to pass by I never reported until I seen a show whereas a craft was tracked from florida to new mexico on this same night and I thought someone should know.
